  "description": "AgentWorkforce slack-relayfile-doctor persona pack — a debugging specialist for the Slack ↔ relayfile ↔ cloud sync/writeback stack. Localizes a symptom to the right layer, confirms root cause with concrete evidence (mount state, the ops API, logs), and prescribes the fix to the owning repo. Install with `agentworkforce install`.",
